WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:06.202
Good evening, family. Thank you for joining me again tonight. Well, we got them.

00:00:06.203 --> 00:00:21.857
I believe the prayers of the people from this channel—and you know, I know there's a lot of other people praying, but we had thousands of people praying last night at about the same time that he was turned in.

00:00:21.858 --> 00:00:29.070
And so, I think it was within the hour. So, I just want to give God some praise that prayer works.

00:00:29.071 --> 00:00:35.423
You know, it's amazing when we all come together; many hands make light work.

00:00:35.424 --> 00:00:42.623
And I'm just thankful for her healing, the wife's healing. What is it, Erica?

00:00:42.624 --> 00:00:54.117
Is that right? Erica's healing. It helps, you know, to catch the person who murdered her husband.

00:00:54.118 --> 00:01:08.452
Praise God that we found him, that there were no other lives lost in this, that the law enforcement did a good job, and that the father had courage enough to turn his son in.

