You know, I thought it was interesting that his heart was convicted enough that he went to his pastor and asked for help and counsel.

00:01:16.717 --> 00:01:27.438
And the pastor said, "Of course, you should turn your son in,"and he held him in his room until the authorities got there because his son was trying to flee.

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:38.076
But I believe because of the prayers of the righteous, because of us praying in agreement that this would be quickly resolved, I believe prayer changes things.

00:01:38.077 --> 00:01:50.719
And what an honor to be a part of this. I'm so thankful that you join me and you take prayer seriously in these last of the last days.

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:57.599
I didn't realize that today the UN was going to have their vote.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:02.648
So, they had their vote today, and I guess it was ahead of schedule.

00:02:02.649 --> 00:02:14.559
I was praying that it was going to happen during the week of the 20th—the 22nd, 23rd—that week, but they held it the day after 9/11 in the UN.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:26.958
Yesterday, I felt it so strong to pray for New York, to pray for the two-state solution and the things that would be voted upon.

00:02:26.959 --> 00:02:37.514
And there were 10 countries that refrained—that sided with Israel—and the rest of the world basically sided against them.

00:02:37.515 --> 00:02:49.759
If you see this list, the ones in green are the ones that voted for a two-state solution.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:03:08.932
So France, Saudi Arabia, and these other nations are going to try to bring more of a framework in the week of the 20th, 21st, 22nd, 23rd—that week.

00:03:08.933 --> 00:03:22.719
So, there's more prayer to be done, but the vote was cast. And so we see where the nations are divided: the ones that are for Israel and the ones that are not.

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:35.955
And it's pretty alarming. I guess it was 10 countries, and they were really countries that didn't have a lot of influence that stood by Israel.

00:03:35.956 --> 00:03:46.473
From what I understand, even Australia voted for a two-state solution, and Canada, and England.

00:03:46.474 --> 00:03:55.853
There were so many that I was shocked to see on that list, very disappointed in it.

00:03:55.854 --> 00:04:07.598
But this is what the Lord warned us was coming—a line that would be drawn in the sand of who is for and who is against.

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:15.573
This is an acceleration of what the Lord said: a September to remember. And boy, it has turned out to be just like the Lord said.

00:04:15.574 --> 00:04:29.679
I don't think I'll ever forget this September, ever, already for what we've seen just in the first 12 or 13 days.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:39.697
Incredible, actually—I mean, for how fast everything has accelerated, even just in this month. But we see the vote.

00:04:39.697 --> 00:04:50.410
Thank God the United States of America stood, just like the Lord said, a Jonathan and David relationship would begin even more in the days ahead.

00:04:50.411 --> 00:04:58.620
But we see that even Mark from Canada voted against it. And this is what the Lord was warning me about Canada.

00:04:58.621 --> 00:05:15.720
I don't know why he shows me certain countries specifically over these areas to pray concerning British Columbia in the days ahead for a great earthquake, for 30,000 casualties from an earthquake.

00:05:15.721 --> 00:05:40.435
And these are the things that I've been praying over. But it's much greater than this, as I was shown in the spirit concerning George—I won't say his last name anymore, but George—and he has a lot of influence, that's what I'll say.

00:05:40.436 --> 00:05:57.578
I saw him having a meeting with the devil. And when I was caught up in the spirit, I was allowed to hear through prayer what was going to transpire in the days ahead, of how they would try to create...

00:05:57.579 --> 00:06:06.799
you know, the Bible says we wrestle not against flesh and blood. Ladies and gentlemen, I understand.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:31.644
Basically, what's happening, what I'm trying to tell you, is that the enemy is trying to come in to wreak havoc in America for a great distraction, for great turbulence to begin—civil unrest, civil wars, things that try to escalate to bring a divide in America.

00:06:31.645 --> 00:06:37.299
And when you're distracted inside, like I said with the ants coming up out of the den...

00:06:37.300 --> 00:06:50.262
and the Lord showed me specifically five major cities out of the ten, a major event that will happen all on the same day.

00:06:50.263 --> 00:07:07.279
All on the same day. Five major cities. He showed me Chicago, Philadelphia, Washington DC, New York, and Boston.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:17.824
These were very... it was a well-thought-out plan. I cannot go into the depth of this right now. The Lord will not allow me to.

00:07:17.825 --> 00:07:51.754
But I ask you as a watchman to help me pray, to help me pray for our beautiful country, that the plans of the wicked would be uncovered by law enforcement, by our Homeland Security, by our FBI, by the sheriff's department and local law enforcement, that they would see, even just have a crack, and be led by the Spirit of God concerning these events that the enemy would try to use to kill, steal, and destroy, and cause havoc in our great nation.

00:07:51.755 --> 00:08:15.633
So, I'm asking you to help me pray even more tonight. We have a lot to pray about, but praying over the repercussions of this vote, of what I've seen in the spirit concerning trying to bring forth this two-state solution, bringing forth the end times at a rapid pace—folks, we're right there.

00:08:15.634 --> 00:08:24.435
Do you all understand? If the peace agreement comes and they start to build the third temple soon, look where we are.

00:08:24.436 --> 00:08:35.278
We are just right at the edge, I told you, at a waterfall edge. And it seems like, as it says, labor pains upon a woman.

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:43.598
