00:08:53.279 --> 00:08:58.724
You know, like the doctor would come in and tell your wife, "Well, you only have this window to get an epidural.

00:08:58.725 --> 00:09:03.512
Why? Because it's too late. It's time to push. It's too late.

00:09:03.513 --> 00:09:07.697
