And a lot of people I know are saying that, and they get so mad at me: "Brandon, we believe the rapture of the church is taking place on the 23rd, and you are wrong."Well, when you're here on the 24th and the 25th, you can come back and continue to pray with me.

00:09:39.516 --> 00:09:45.453
I'm just telling you that's how bold I am about that he is not coming on the 23rd.

00:09:45.454 --> 00:10:00.319
I believe we have a great harvest and a great shaking to awaken the body of Christ, a window of opportunity for the church to bring in the lost as quickly as possible.

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:12.574
He doesn't want that any man should perish, but all come to repentance. And this is one last call, for a great shaking is coming.

00:10:12.575 --> 00:10:24.152
As I heard the angels above, from the west to the east yelling, "Woe, woe, woe, America!

00:10:24.153 --> 00:10:34.541
A great shaking is no longer coming. It is here."That's what I heard.

00:10:34.542 --> 00:10:45.104
They sounded like thunder as I was sitting, and I came out, and the Lord said, "Sit."I have a word."And I told my wife, "Get the recorder.

