00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:20.146
But as I had an open-eye vision, I saw the clouds, and I could see the thunder and the clouds shaking.

00:11:20.147 --> 00:11:24.889
I don't know how else to describe it, how you see a cloud shaking, but this is what I was seeing.

00:11:24.890 --> 00:11:36.799
The clouds vibrated as they said, 'Woe, woe, woe, America.'And it shook.

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:42.879
I could feel the vibrations coming off of it, and it went from west to east.

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:53.119
And I saw a great earthquake taking place in California. I saw a great volcano getting ready to go off.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:12:06.393
I saw these plots and these five major cities plus these ten, but five are worse than the other five.

00:12:06.394 --> 00:12:12.071
Okay, you have five major cities that are hit hard, and five that are not as hard.

00:12:12.072 --> 00:12:23.859
They spent most of their money on the five, and that's all. I don't feel peace; I cannot say anything else.

00:12:23.860 --> 00:12:34.638
But you must take this seriously and pray over our beautiful nation.

00:12:34.639 --> 00:12:39.759
There's a shaking to awaken. Everybody said, 'Brandon, did you see Charlie?

00:12:39.760 --> 00:13:02.891
Did you see all these things?'I saw a major minister who would be taken out with a bullet, and it would be called 'the shot heard 'round the world.'The shot heard 'round the world.

00:13:02.892 --> 00:13:10.016
He said it—the Lord said it to me several times. This was in my private prayer time. He said, 'A great shaking is coming.

00:13:10.017 --> 00:13:30.819
It will try to bring fear in the hearts of men so they won't have revival in buildings—afraid to go, afraid to gather in the country, afraid to gather in public events because of what the enemy has in store to disrupt what God is doing.

00:13:30.820 --> 00:13:42.398
God is not going to try; God is going to do. He is going to have a major revival, and there's no devil in hell that will hold it back.

00:13:42.399 --> 00:14:23.119
But it will take us having a backbone like a crowbar to stand in the gap and say, "Thus far, Satan, and no further."Do you understand?'So, as I saw these events taking place on college campuses, at tailgate parties with major events, a man in a green uniform in Denver, and I've seen strategic locations on the Vegas Strip where the big pyramid is, where the water fountains go off, and more events.

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:34.559
The Lord warned me to pray over three men. It's not just one; it's three.

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:49.119
I saw three men strategically marked. One is Don Jr., and that's why I told you you must pray for this man.

00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:56.397
It's very serious to pray a hedge around and about him. It was nighttime when I saw this happen.

00:14:56.398 --> 00:15:00.313
Now, if it happens in the daytime, I don't want to help the enemy out.

00:15:00.314 --> 00:15:07.603
