00:15:07.604 --> 00:15:15.501
He said, 'Pray for him.'He tells me these things and He visits me, and I feel His presence so strong.

00:15:15.502 --> 00:15:29.119
He says, 'Pray for this man. Pray for leaders in the church. Pray for this because the enemy has a plan to kill, steal, and destroy. Pray for Donald Trump's health.

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:43.599
Pray for him, for his heart, and for his veins.'I saw this, ladies and gentlemen, before it came out in the news that they were checking all this stuff.

00:15:43.600 --> 00:15:47.218
You can't get that by the flesh; you get that by the Spirit of God.

00:15:47.219 --> 00:15:51.274
And I'm not listening to a devil; I'm listening to the Holy Spirit.

00:15:51.274 --> 00:15:59.919
I have communion, I pray, and I seek His face. And as you seek Him, you will find Him. If you knock, the door will be opened unto you.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:13.752
He said, 'I will do nothing on this earth without revealing it to my prophetic voices first.'Now, I do not consider myself a prophet; I consider myself a watchman, somebody who is called to pray.

00:16:13.753 --> 00:16:25.984
Now, I know there's other prophetic ministries on YouTube, and I bless them, but I'm just telling you, Brandon Biggs, I feel that my wife—the Lord's even told us to call our ministry Prayer Changes Things.

00:16:25.985 --> 00:16:36.526
And I couldn't call it 'Prayer Changes Things Church'because there was already one there, so I said 'Foundation.'So, I said, 'Prayer Changes Things.'That's what we're about.

00:16:36.527 --> 00:16:47.033
