00:18:12.138 --> 00:18:15.886
Every single one of us—not one of us is better than the other.

00:18:15.887 --> 00:18:19.302
God's called every single one of you to do something big for Him.

00:18:19.303 --> 00:18:30.700
I was a janitor for fifteen years, and I was looked down upon for a lot of my life, with learning disabilities all through school and all the things that I've been through.

00:18:30.701 --> 00:18:38.677
