00:20:23.261 --> 00:20:36.541
this ten percent is maybe less to sow into the thousand years to reap that, but I want to sow into the thousand years.

00:20:36.542 --> 00:20:45.359
What I am doing on this side of the earth right now is so that I reap a great harvest for the thousand-year reign.

00:20:45.360 --> 00:21:05.439
