00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:49.119
When you get real with God, He'll become real to you. That's a better way to say it.

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:54.656
He'll become real to your inner man, because you're not trying to be something that you're not.

00:21:54.657 --> 00:22:00.954
He sees right through it. He sees right through it. You are not pretending.

00:22:00.955 --> 00:22:12.158
