00:22:12.159 --> 00:22:20.399
Maybe even your wife or your husband doesn't see it, but the Father sees it all, and you're not fooling nobody.

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:29.788
You're not fooling Him. The motives of the heart. And that's why I say, that's why I believe David says, "Search me and know me.

00:22:29.789 --> 00:22:43.473
Create in me a clean heart, O God."I want you to really search yourself.

00:22:43.474 --> 00:22:52.591
That's why I do it all the time. I do it. I do it continually. "God, show me, create in me a clean heart.

00:22:52.592 --> 00:23:00.189
Purify me. Purify my heart, Lord, through the refining refiner's fire, that You burn out the chaff.

00:23:00.190 --> 00:23:09.359
Burn out the trash in my life, and expose the darkness, the hidden things that maybe I don't even realize.

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:18.639
